Class SlyceSearchTaskListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.slyce.sdk.SlyceSearchTaskListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SlyceSearchTaskListener

    public abstract class SlyceSearchTaskListenerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements SlyceSearchTaskListener
    Adapter class for SlyceSearchTaskListener. This class overrides all methods with an empty implementation. This is useful if you only want to implement some and not all of the methods in the associated interface.
